          "text": "fit in",
          "colorize": true
        },
        {
          "text": " with the other students"
        }
      ],
      "tips": "'Fit in' is about social belonging and acceptance, not just physical space. It describes feeling part of a community."
    },
    {
      "word": "lost touch with",
      "wordType": "phrasal verb",
      "definition": [
        {
          "text": "To "
        },
        {
          "text": "no longer communicate",
          "highlight": true
        },
        {
          "text": " or have "
        },
        {
          "text": "contact with someone",
          "highlight2": true
        },
        {
          "text": " you once knew well"
        }
      ],
      "arabicMeaning": "فقد التواصل مع / انقطع عن",
      "synonyms": [
        "lose contact with",
        "drift apart from"
      ],
      "example": [
        {
          "text": "After moving abroad, I "
